en_562074_0	The tattoo team of the Corps of Sri Lanka Military Police (SLCMP) at the request of the authorities in the Ministry of Women’s & Children’s Affairs contributed to the commemoration of the World Children’s Day, held at Colombo Vihara Mahadevi Park on Thursday (5).
en_562074_1	Sri Lanka Rupavahini Corporation organized the events in cooperation with the Ministry, Colombo Municipal Council and other civil organizations.
en_562074_2	The Army’s display of acrobatics and drills attracted the huge crowd attending the occasion.
